[quote=“kronixz, post:3, topic:418789”][quote author=JavaTC link=topic=521330.msg3788092#msg3788092 date=1319061936]
That usually means it can’t find the cache. Edit the directory to the C: drive and host the cache off dropbox. It’s typically in signlink.java.
[/quote]
it could also download the cache from “cachedownloader”.java[/quote]

Not all sources have that but that’s another place, but the load directory is in signlink.
